Package: obsession
Source: obsession (20140608-2)
Version: 20140608-2+b1
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Fabien Givors <f+debian@chezlefab.net>
Installed-Size: 350
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.4), libcairo2 (>= 1.2.4), libgdk-pixbuf2.0-0 (>= 2.22.0), libglib2.0-0 (>= 2.31.8), libgtk2.0-0 (>= 2.14.0)
Recommends: gnome-icon-theme
Section: x11
Priority: extra
Homepage: https://bitbucket.org/fabriceT/obsession
Description: Session management helpers for lightweight desktop environments
 This package provides the following tools:
  * obsession-logout displays a dialog where you can choose if you want to quit
    the session, power off, suspend or hibernate the computer.
  * obsession-exit: this is the command line version of obsession-logout.
  * xdg-autostart start automatically programs defined in /etc/xdg/autostart and
    ~/.config/autostart.
